{"tid":648323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三星深圳廠方遷往東南亞   蘇州外商投資斷崖式暴跌","createTime":"2018-04-30T14:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T02:57:15.000Z","uid":39464,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5b595ceda92401bec736fbb868ab91a3defca580","tid":648323,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:43:19.000Z","msg":"【三星深圳廠方遷往東南亞】<br />\n【蘇州外商投資斷崖式暴跌】<br />\n<br />\n三星在深圳的通訊設備生產廠房，月初開始已逐步辭退三百多名員工，到現在已停止運作。好像三星這樣外資企業廠房關閉，是否個別事件呢?<br />\n<br />\n一直以外資企業主導的蘇州，自2013年外資企業的工業投資創出1200億歷史高峰後，就逐年下降，到去年已累積跌了30%，至今年一、二月份，蘇州總體的工業投資，就只剩下99億元人民幣，跌幅比去年同期超過了五成。這些數據跟過去幾年多間大型外資企業從蘇州撤離中國，相當吻合。<br />\n<br />\n至於蘇州和深圳相似的地方，就是過去五年工業投資佔比下降期間，地產投資就逐年上升。<br />\n<br />\n#外資大撤退<br />\n#三星唔玩了<br />\n#蘇州今非昔比<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1704270243050788/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1704270243050788%2F&d=SoHoN3jx8HdMuib1ab2rs6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=8a2649a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1704270243050788/</a>"},{"pid":"13c0ef0d35f2f9fceae11f3c386814729cbc4f21","tid":648323,"uid":176111,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:45:22.000Z","msg":"蚛蟈又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"640f53c772be666edf7e11affa9ddf2e13c079c8","tid":648323,"uid":30169,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:45:57.000Z","msg":"蘇州總體的工業投資，就只剩下99億元人民幣，跌幅比去年同期超過了五成<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013b91a511674faf803c0e9caa6dd087c3af5fcb","tid":648323,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:46:25.000Z","msg":"求仁得仁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji